---
title: Crumbed Haloumi Burger with Kumara Fries & Caramelised Onions
description: Serve up a hearty burger with this version made with a golden "patty" of crumbed haloumi! A smear of smokey aioli and sweet caramelised onions turns this veggie dinner into a taste sensation.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/crumbed-haloumi-burger-kumara-fries-c21f9249.jpg
